{"tid":974190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎留個言尋找下失左聯絡既人","createTime":"2019-01-08T16:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T17:11:37.000Z","uid":86628,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3123d8979d21ae221069dd93c778c8a4f1c9b368","tid":974190,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:26:54.000Z","msg":"我以前玩過靈劍江湖0406 （04-05年左右）<br />\n個名叫 心大心<br />\n以前做過掌門 無幾個月<br />\n但有周圍同女仔傾計交換電話黎傾計<br />\n<br />\n以前抄低曬對方江湖名同電話落本薄<br />\n成日打過去搵人傾計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我傳返d法力比你"},{"pid":"b7e461afb91a754b15b97a4c7a78449c750fa9b9","tid":974190,"uid":24519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"Ruby915"},{"pid":"9b8d7dd075c5375a64b450552256a264acef3613","tid":974190,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"好細個玩跑online識過一個女仔叫畈畈李<br />\n澳門人黎<br />\n之後唔記得點解斷左聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然冇聯絡咁耐而家都唔熟了"},{"pid":"c20cf0bb978a09c61a3a1999b2d9d3578b98e987","tid":974190,"uid":119401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:01:36.000Z","msg":"江湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好似200x年玩過下<br />\n有晚凌晨玩過一個唔記得咗名<br />\n入到去無乜人就是但搵個人密佢，叫佢送少少物品比我，點知佢比咗個電話我叫我打比佢講..<br />\n傻傻下打過去講我想要咩，唔知點樣傾傾下就做咗情侶定咩...要我每日打比佢..<br />\n<br />\n重點嚟喇..之後佢話個江湖係佢老豆開比個佢玩，然後就有個叫&ldquo;月下老人&rdquo;嘅站長就現身密我叫我好好咁對佢個女..唔係對我唔客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬..玩遊戲姐可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我傾咗兩三日就冇玩到個江湖就完咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98acba8b8f176fa23402bdc98333db77a72be8d","tid":974190,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:36:36.000Z","msg