15.000Z","msg":"好細個玩忍豆2，我ac名叫pantene1，同人交換電話，跟住有一排同成班人一齊傾有男有女，之後唔記得咩就冇再傾lu"},{"pid":"c5739fed3b56779d698ba709d3cabd0749d348e4","tid":974190,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cbb7f3cb91d30c61dbfe113f7dd7d72034ac60","tid":974190,"uid":219650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"留名睇下有無人會尋找我"},{"pid":"b51ed696cd200d95600dc7599b149e4a6a225bc3","tid":974190,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"著長花裙白波鞋<br />\n頭先（10 jan）夜晚9點半左右係荔景上地鐵葵芳落車<br />\n<br />\n妳身上耳環和手袋的藍色簡直係黑白世界中的色彩<br />\n衣著配飾別樹一格<br />\n淡妝上劃上鳳尾眼線<br />\n只是短短兩三分鐘的相處<br />\n念念不忘"},{"pid":"f3acab2a4498df5542c7853fcba3ac4da31420b2","tid":974190,"uid":62899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T19:57:07.000Z","msg":"以前玩跑 online 識左個叫 ed池 既人<br />\n佢勁過我成日都等埋我先一齊衝線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中交換過聯絡方法<br />\n所以當時一有得用電腦就會上線睇佢係唔係到之後一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多數都撞正佢上線<br />\n佢又肯同我兩個人玩吹下水先難得<br />\n不過日子耐左<br />\n愈黎愈少玩<br />\n好耐冇上線冇開跑啦<br />\n唔知你仲記唔記得我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480ae1414f074e96915f386078b41a8558afdc30","tid":974190,"uid":165388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T20:09:29.000Z","msg":"想搵返以前小學升旗隊嘅一個女仔 叫凱欣"},{"pid":"4969c74175926bb07e8ead9409fe842c3f696191","tid":974190,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T20:12:54.000Z","msg":"飄流<br />\n水色ser 叫ROY<br />\n見到搵返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5e809ab9f8c53ce39b2cacaae16efb9e2b6f8f","tid":974190,"uid":62899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T20:26:09.000Z","msg":"仲有我唯一既樹窿Treetree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直keep得好好<br />\n好多野淨係同你傾<br />\n但有段時間大家都唔係幾方便搵大家<br />\n後來愈搵愈少<br />\n之後你就開始消失了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟你去左邊<br />\n唔知你出左咩事做乜無啦啦消失咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好想繼續同你傾心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你幾時可以同我再傾應下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}